    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >想了解《镀金天命》以及更多 Hooded Horse 策略类游戏信息与福利，QQ频道搜索:Hooded Horse 加入我们 或关注 bilibili 官方账号 @HoodedHorse。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《镀金天命》是一款以工业时代为背景的大战略游戏，玩家将建立帝国、推动革命，以一己之力重塑整个社会。快来操纵外交、发展工业、决战沙场，带领国家走向荣耀吧！ </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>真实球形地图</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2189430/extras/eb81a5f2b093df9d4b0bb4098591ca38.poster.avif?t=1771524822\" width=780 height=434 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2189430/extras/eb81a5f2b093df9d4b0bb4098591ca38.webm?t=1771524822\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2189430/extras/eb81a5f2b093df9d4b0bb4098591ca38.mp4?t=1771524822\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以数百万个六边形构筑19至20世纪的世界样貌，真实呈现生态系与地貌特徵。这并不是平面地图，而是1：1真实比例呈现所有国家的立体球形地图。你的位置将影响战术决策，全球策略也会带来重大影响。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >地形与环境将直接影响军事部署与工业发展</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自由放置城市、建筑、铁路，见证国土工业化进程</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >发售即内建编辑器与Mod支援，发挥天马行空的想像力，创造属于你的历史—不论是平行时空，还是奇幻大陆</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>战争艺术大师</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2189430/extras/4d5480c0ccb0c70f1f001d7fe3e41157.poster.avif?t=1771524822\" width=780 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2189430/extras/4d5480c0ccb0c70f1f001d7fe3e41157.webm?t=1771524822\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2189430/extras/4d5480c0ccb0c70f1f001d7fe3e41157.mp4?t=1771524822\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在详尽的军事模拟中直接指挥你的军队。缜密的规划、部队的组成和高效的后勤都能为你增加优势。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >微观操控单支部队，或委任电脑执行宏观战略</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >调整军队编制、管理补给线、争夺交通枢纽，让战争得以持续</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >拥抱科技突破，动态调整军事策略应对时代变革</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>工业帝国创始者</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2189430/extras/e663d16fd7afef6b2fa98765462c8555.poster.avif?t=1771524822\" width=780 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2189430/extras/e663d16fd7afef6b2fa98765462c8555.webm?t=1771524822\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2189430/extras/e663d16fd7afef6b2fa98765462c8555.mp4?t=1771524822\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以精密的生产与贸易模拟称霸全球经济。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >建立跨国生产体系，操纵大宗商品供需关係</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >上百种特色工厂塑造国民经济命脉</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >推行劳工改革、医疗体系、徵兵制度等社会变革</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >应对动态历史事件，在危机与机遇中治国</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>文明演进模拟器</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >引领工业化浪潮中的社会文化的更替</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >管理宗教传播、人口迁徙与文化融合进程</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >将农民转化为产业工人、工程师或职业军人，完成转型</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >平衡诉求历史真实党派的利益诉求，玩转政治博弈</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>完善的创意工坊支持</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2189430/extras/4617421907036c582d1fc3b19c833d46.poster.avif?t=1771524822\" width=780 height=440 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2189430/extras/4617421907036c582d1fc3b19c833d46.webm?t=1771524822\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2189430/extras/4617421907036c582d1fc3b19c833d46.mp4?t=1771524822\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《镀金天命》配备了强大的编辑器和完整的mod支持，让您可以自由地重写历史或创建自己的替代场景。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自由重划国界、改造地形、创造全新剧本</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Steam创意工坊支持，从微调到全面改写都由你来决定</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >塑造你的世界和你的规则，每局都是独一无二的战略体验</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>历史名臣登场</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与栩栩如生的历史人物共撰史诗</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >任命具备独特能力的军政要员与科技先驱</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >鲜明艺术风格呈现决策者与民众群像，带来鲜活的游戏体验</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用编辑器创建自订角色加入游戏</p></li></ul>",
